WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Can you sing, Dad?

00:03.000 --> 00:07.000
No, I can't. Why do you ask?

00:07.000 --> 00:12.000
Because we have singing today at school.

00:12.000 --> 00:15.000
Can you ride a bike, Dad?

00:15.000 --> 00:18.000
Yes, I can.

00:18.000 --> 00:20.000
Can you cook?

00:20.000 --> 00:23.000
Yes, I can.

00:23.000 --> 00:26.000
Can you speak Chinese?

00:26.000 --> 00:29.000
No, I can't.

00:29.000 --> 00:32.000
Can you teach me?

00:32.000 --> 00:37.000
OK, I can teach you Chinese after school.

00:37.000 --> 00:39.000
Thanks.

00:39.000 --> 00:42.000
Have a good day at school.

00:42.000 --> 00:45.000
And please be careful.

